            The bremsstrahlung spectrum-weighted average yield of
            reaction sum [189Os(g,p) + 190Os(g,np)].
DECAY-DATA (75-RE-188,,DG,155.0)
            Data from text on page 1116 of PAN,88,1115,2025.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) The statistical error was about 10%. The
            additional contribution to the overall error due to
            the uncertainty in the shape of the bremsstrahlung
            gamma-ray spectrum was estimated at about 5%.
